title: Bemyself
lyrics:
I know that I can't be a few
I'll be myself
Be myself
I'm told to be over them all
I can teach myself

Teach myself



But I'm old, I can feel that it's true

I believe myself

Believe myself



And I know it'll be over soon

I can see myself

See myself



See myself, see myself, see myself

See myself, see myself, see myself



I'm trapped, but I'm trapped in a booth

I can free myself

Free myself



And I'll talk but you know there's no use

I can hear myself

Hear myself



The road's blocked, I can tell that we've stopped

I believe myself

Believe myself



And I know if I'm moving on up

I can be myself

Be myself



Be myself, be myself, be myself

Be myself, be myself, be myself

Be myself, be myself, be myself

Be myself, be myself, be myself
